{
  "id": "RAW_e9fe2e47",
  "title": "我被骗了？更新 iOS26 后，发现液态玻璃之外的改版居然有惊喜",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMjgzNDgzOQ==&mid=2247532491&idx=1&sn=fd63165f4ed1a67334eebbac13e3c2e7",
  "date": "2025-12-16 00:20:00",
  "author": "体验进阶",
  "siteName": "体验进阶",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8211eee3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUzDNI6O6hCFOCLdZ0cxwHelc2bL9aFBYaXakRX0t5Gicq6EoxopA4MAibAUtAYXvLMYkmvus0DJPd0UqtpibIDRUg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">上次我从专业角度分析了液态玻璃设计的优劣后，引发不少争论：<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMjgzNDgzOQ==&amp;mid=2247530948&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b33974efcb0b620be5ca998747be3978&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"一半人喜欢一半人讨厌？深入分析iOS26液态玻璃到底好不好\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">一半人喜欢一半人讨厌？深入分析iOS26液态玻璃到底好不好</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">由于我个人是真的不太喜欢视觉干扰，所以一直拖到前不久才更新 iOS 26。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">然而更新用了1个礼拜后，我感觉自己被网上的媒体舆论骗了……</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">iOS 26 虽然拿液态玻璃当宣传卖点，但设计改版远不止于此。如果抛开液态玻璃不谈，其它方面做得还挺有诚意，甚至有些地方能给我惊喜。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">我居然会产生“苹果真有种</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\">，终于肯把陈年老规范改了”的感觉。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">接下来就分享6个我认为值得一提的设计点，大家看看感觉如何。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\">1. 闹钟超大字号</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048823\" data-ratio=\"1.0675925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=765c0e19&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCFOCLdZ0cxwHelc2bL9aFBYBnD4hB5bSqFSl51LtH9hWXmFJjXx5RrWPhO0YlBniaZibvtj5nlpBm4Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">对于我这种高度近视来说，每天早上关闹钟，都要眯着眼睛把屏幕怼到脸上才行。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">苹果设计师终于发现了这个痛点，把字号改到了我不戴眼镜也能远远看清的尺寸。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">这个设计点</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">真的把我感动到了！</span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048774\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"510\" style=\"width:216px;height:216px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=50667d06&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNbFpBvia13bXRO6J2RqCoJvO1CtBJBxrWpZ9zOtYsyG4RSDE9jAibKUnA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">一个好的设计并不需要什么特别的专业技能，只需要抓住那些隐蔽而重要的痛点就行。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\">2. 标题栏按钮统一</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">苹果的页面和吸底弹窗的标题栏设计，一直有不统一的问题。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">有时关闭按钮是右上角的图标，有时是文字按钮：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048775\" data-ratio=\"0.5018518518518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=485f9721&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNRT1YPnuibdAGwBfpYwNPzEQLHfpQ64nD136HmbyhoHLoeEd1NHTfaNQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">很多App也跟着苹果学，搞出了类似的标题栏统一问题：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048776\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=86dfb01c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CN6mgY5c5eS67zZzxXvPfja6L7nrVIhFLJEyRdPicfwPSTicPd367g5yhA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhk812k71369\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhk812kshk8\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">百度云盘</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048777\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=08f29995&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNFQBWtHAWiaIJ3el5Aic4fec1aTJVDzfevBtSxBemQicD2aycXVWolELvA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhk812k71369\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhk812kshk8\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: center;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">知乎</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">iOS 26 终于把这个问题解决了——去掉文字按钮，一律用图标：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048779\" data-ratio=\"0.5018518518518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=560b87b9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNfN7oNS0ewhvMCqRaq5l3RxFwNIjf67MqUyLa1FMCZmIU5Tic8gibjMuQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">对设计师来说，确定按钮用什么文案再不用多想了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">对开发来说，可以一套组件走遍天下了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">对用户来说，刚开始不习惯，但操作区域大了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">一举三得，好好好。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048780\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-w=\"300\" data-type=\"gif\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=94304ce5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNJiauYEiaVXh3MWQLt0nZpYJ4W7MdvvZhANlPPlDwk9jKbAdxaYvMD7cg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\">3. 菜单图标放到左边</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">绝大多数的菜单设计，包括隔壁 Material Design，菜单项的图标都在左侧，跟文字连在一起：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span data-mpa-action-id=\"mhk8k56xrmi\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2037037037037037\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=afee047e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCHvCNvM31ib2GOMe7r7zzCu7DhjY0htoiaHJck4r0iakDNjxd6RbuR2QPhdg8gN1WTPkiane2ZuUZYN9A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D12\"></span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhk8k5691l72\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">安卓原生系统</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">唯有 iOS 不知怎么想的，之前一直把图标放到右边，跟文字“隔岸相望”……</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">现在 iOS 26 终于改过来了，图标一致跟文字一起放到左侧了：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048781\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"720\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=550856e2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNR8vdiaOKhb0pkXgzgP4fC79MuVvXiaUTloxL29fg8nYXUsZLBbD3XA3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048782\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"720\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cf8491e1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNdW0R2nE98JpISoSk7Tgb5IibuSZeX1sNaWCdRU8Z1EMziaMBkMvyEBCw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">从视线扫描的角度来看，图标放到左侧肯定是更好的。因为用户可以一次把图标和文字一起扫描了，不用跳转太远。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048783\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"720\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6f0a7a67&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNgR5m0Yt9c18zdAp9KeFk1wYx7UwLxgdUaAcuMTY6WXeYpceHzszWicg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">现在 iOS 26 总算改正常了，这也算是可喜可贺吧。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null,&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\">4. 原地弹出菜单</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">之前点击图标后弹出的菜单，都在图标底部显示。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.287962962962963\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=63c9005e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUzDNI6O6hCF9Bz2Exf2EQn1E2CCBwPLy0btYz9icKgcTicLAM3DWJpKOaHjOwIdvhYOkkyXVRibEycZswyHs4umibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D12\"></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">其实绝大多数 App 都是这么设计的：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100048784\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=291e1ea9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CN3Pibe6WLvCeX0OX44Q49hNZ1EvzyZicsrHRNa1Hsx17I9Zic24UuWSRIg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">但是 iOS 26 让弹窗把原来的按钮替换掉，这样可以节约空间，把弹窗做得更大一些。而且相比吸底菜单或弹窗，这样操作起来更加方便，因为手指的移动距离更短。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048787\" data-ratio=\"1\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=183f2e3e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CN1TvCkiaSibrcVNIrn4IkXHo3DoVjI70mgEepE1iamfQLJKdqfOyBuKAiaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048785\" data-ratio=\"1\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0bed1f70&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNfWUGLHvkr1aBX9SicEymKooz6ykCbLf5hvAicuAgeBm5ZRNJw7Vibf03g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">甚至二次确认弹窗，也能用这种形式：</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048786\" data-ratio=\"1\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b14612f2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNLicmUD6lpTAQtK6M0ubxbE6pEP3FD6E1BqkVIiaur6CmnTUN1aFKGyuQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">这个设计比之前更简洁，除了研发成本更高之外，好像没啥问题？</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">这让我想到了2019年自己在知乎分享过 Material Design 的千赞文。他们是把菜单，叠在了下拉框上面，设计思路有异曲同工之处：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048788\" data-ratio=\"0.9027777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d2a793e6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNkqAzgMh7RN6jib3SEVlb2slQLTqR8GQdFWs7gQAb3JgLUygTTN9S4CQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">上图来源：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/24887891\" target=\"_blank\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/24887891</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">但是，这个设计在 Material Design 3 被取消了：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100048791\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0018518518518518\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=946f9e85&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CN0YQOCk3AZNHXhHda36K3gtJ3V5qGs62rzaBMQOOO3dZDKGXeGzoU1Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">上图来源：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\"><a href=\"https://m3.material.io/components/menus/specs\" target=\"_blank\">https://m3.material.io/components/menus/specs</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">iOS 26 的这个菜单设计，也不知道能坚持多久，让我们拭目以待吧。</span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\">5. 搜索框吸底</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">iOS 以前跟</span><span leaf=\"\">大部分App一样，都是把搜索框放到顶部，有时还藏起来。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100048792\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8571428571428571\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"560\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b00d93ef&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNmBQV40yjIRicF9QXics5ZhicO7KaKAeZxuAtpuA9tB16oxB3PiboL0gnXA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">现在 iOS 26 里很多列表页都把搜索框放到页面底部了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100048795\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.249074074074074\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b5a91a2c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CN3CIHbRrxZamWX41icrH3Oy1Zcep4QovPhZGKa7fFBl8GDwTFTHPCibLQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048793\" data-ratio=\"1.252085264133457\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=04acd067&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNGuaOSlOUu0sj6OQzZ8hEibNiaU8xCN7EicGibPjynIFbdE2icKefgnxYVUw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100048794\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.249074074074074\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=420f8225&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNCI4cD5WHgTHIKFMug6NvnYKAZ2ERaK5Bt0Ala5hwXkAMSWxWyNdL2Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">这个设计还挺颠覆的，如果我平时这么出设计方案，估计十有八九评审不通过吧。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100048796\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.74\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"width:266px;height:197px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=064d7811&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNNibOvUE580HTnSS6OviafVLzFdLjR3OuNovIZCxIpuibI2ictBflJDwutQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">iOS 26 敢这么做，一方面说明苹果给设计团队的权限不低，至少比大部分国内公司强；另一方面，也是因为 iOS 之前的改版已经做过好几次实验了，人家是循序渐进的。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">iOS 15 就给浏览器做过一个很大的创新，把浏览器的地址栏从顶部移到底部了。老实说我还挺喜欢这个设计，因为这样我才可以单手操作。但别家浏览器都没跟着学，可惜啊：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span data-mpa-action-id=\"mhkciqe818xd\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhkgyhdk20tr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.1666666666666665\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 46%;flex-basis: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"720\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d31d141b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FUzDNI6O6hCFRC8FlC5L6xicr8hVL64QpkcRKbMvque3KCVKL4GB3cW5joCsEic4fSeRkLT5qX0tF1r9pFRUAiaqIg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D6\"></p>\n  <span mpa-font-style=\"mhkciqdkq6u\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\"><span leaf=\"\">上图来源：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMjgzNDgzOQ==&amp;mid=2247498984&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=d2aa997e57ed859360970d0aedf647c4&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"iOS15一些神奇的新设计，忍不住要分享\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">iOS15一些神奇的新设计，忍不住要分享</a></span></span>\n  <p></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">后来 iOS 18 备受争议的相册改版，搜索入口虽然在右上角，但输入状态时，搜索框是在底部的。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100048797\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7574074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=800aa78e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNshakIsu1ibO7fma7L0z7TYJib69r24uUibv12xJJS3myj70VmSrpEOI9Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a9f3f94c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUzDNI6O6hCF9Bz2Exf2EQn1E2CCBwPLyrWIl2yj6xcG9FoAkmJWP9tOxiczveskic5ibMkPOxQsIc1UBu4Cu8xhcg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D19\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span data-mpa-action-id=\"mhkcm5ck1ykm\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhkcm5bvpql\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\"><span leaf=\"\">上图来源：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMjgzNDgzOQ==&amp;mid=2247528401&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=8a1e8f72e0da2a99abfe5b7fe8f47892&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"iOS18相册是苹果的设计倒退吗？\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">iOS18相册是苹果的设计倒退吗？</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">可能发现用户对这种底部输入框的反馈还行，终于决定在 iOS 26 大胆一把，将搜索框都统一吸底了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">不论如何，这种愿意为了设计创新而花费数年时间长期探索的精神，还是值得钦佩的。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\">6. 滑动选择</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">iOS 26 的底导航和菜单，点下后都可以很顺畅地滑动：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100048799\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7506950880444856\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=20f0153c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNce38KqBrXFRH5qxeiaibYKXPdv2Lcfbc5I2Kj3IR4vh97KgY7yqBQBAQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100048798\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7506950880444856\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6acbfc38&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNTdPpqic1q5MKPKxLvB9ZWS4pT6iaLp8Vu1FEoshiaLeX0yg9Ow8GxrOgg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">虽然这样看起来很酷炫，但我觉得最有价值的点，还是在于操作的便利性。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">我自己经常做用户测试，就发现用户在使用PC端时，如果不知道选哪个选项，就会把光标放到上面来回游移，直到做出决定为止。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048800\" data-ratio=\"0.38181818181818183\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"990\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2994011d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNxG1qQSxCiaNiaLpSeHz9G4P7iaexACoW389jYEQ7UlC8BXBdruPbabicMw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">这种“点兵点将”的行为，其实是人类的本能。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">可惜触摸屏不允许我们这么使用，通常点到哪个就是哪个，不能更换。所以线上用户测试，移动端比PC端要更难做，你无法在屏幕上看到用户犹豫的过程。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">但是 iOS 26 增加的这个滑动选择的方式，却给了用户一个犹豫的空间。可以按下后切换选择，或者按下后移出反悔。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100048801\" data-ratio=\"0.2632066728452271\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2f881679&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FUzDNI6O6hCEIEcHCCKSgGHCXYGrPk5CNc8JX5zt32aK4Us431zBxHNrBo2mZtlAQQBI99iaFCUYZ9PUlM9f14Yg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">为了这种微末的细节，而增加那么多研发和设计成本，值得吗？</span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">除了苹果之外，全球找不到几家公司能做这样的探索了。好在，他们真的愿意花成本去探索这些别的公司做不到的事情，而不是完全躺平/吃老本。所以，哪怕他们作为先驱者探索错了方向，我觉得都还是应该鼓励。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\">总结一下</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">一口气介绍了6个设计点，来投个票吧：</span></p>\n   <p class=\"mp_vote_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-vote class=\"js_editor_vote_card js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_vote_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpvote\" data-supervoteid=\"478147637\" data-expiretime=\"1767196819\" data-votesubject=\"[{&quot;type&quot;:1,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;如果只能留下一个设计点，你最想留哪个？&quot;,&quot;options&quot;:[{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;闹钟超大字号&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;cnt&quot;:0},{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;标题栏按钮统一&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;cnt&quot;:0},{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;菜单图标放到左边&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;cnt&quot;:0},{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;搜索框吸底&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;cnt&quot;:0},{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;滑动选择&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;cnt&quot;:0},{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;都不感兴趣&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;cnt&quot;:0}],&quot;total_cnt&quot;:0}]\" data-delflag=\"0\" data-fail=\"0\"></mp-common-vote></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">这6个设计点挺不一样的：1是包容性设计、2是统一规范、3是阅读便捷性、4是操作便捷性、5是容错性。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一次改版能容纳这么多花样的设计亮点，超过绝大多数App的“换皮”改版了。所以，我还是觉得苹果的设计是很强的，这家公司对设计也是比较重视的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">相对而言，液态玻璃真的是一个太不值得一提的设计点了，这更像是一种技术亮点或宣传噱头，并不能真正体现苹果的设计实力。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">有时候真是应了那句话：“善战者无赫赫之功。”</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">那些显而易见的功绩，经常是华而不实；而</span><span leaf=\"\">真正做得好的地方，往往短期看不出效果。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">成大事，真的要有定力有恒心，相信时间会证明一切。</span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章深度分析了 iOS 26 在液态玻璃之外的六项 UI/UX 设计改进，强调了其在细节优化和用户体验创新方面的努力和价值。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章深度分析了 iOS 26 在液态玻璃之外的六项 UI/UX 设计改进，强调了其在细节优化和用户体验创新方面的努力和价值。",
  "summary": "本文作者从一个资深产品设计师的视角，详细解读了 iOS 26 更新中，除了备受争议的“液态玻璃”之外的六大有惊喜的设计改进。这些改进包括：闹钟大字号的无障碍设计、标题栏按钮统一化提升一致性、菜单图标左置优化视线扫描、原地弹出菜单提升操作便捷性、搜索框吸底以适应单手操作趋势，以及滑动选择提供用户犹豫空间。作者肯定了苹果在这些细节上投入的研发和设计成本，认为这些看似细微的调整，实则体现了苹果对用户痛点的洞察、设计规范的坚持以及对创新探索的精神。当然，这些创新也可能带来一定的用户学习成本和适应期，但其长期价值远比表面的液态玻璃更能体现其真正的设计实力。",
  "mainPoints": [
